title: Orlando FreeFall: Crump says teen's death is 'worst tragedy captured on video' other than George Floyd - Fox News

description: Ben Crump, an attorney for the family of a teenager who died after falling off of the Orlando FreeFall on March 24 is calling the incident “the worst tragedy captured on video that I've ever seen” other than the death of George Floyd.
